             sworn. - I am journeyman to Mr. 
               <persName id="t18000528-12-person187">
                  William 
                  Fairbrother
               <interp inst="t18000528-12-person187" type="surname" value="Fairbrother"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000528-12-person187" type="given" value="William"></interp>
